      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>vegan mayo</strong> and <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a bowl with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>honey </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)– this is your <strong>sweet & spicy mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
