        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> remaining white wine vinegar</strong> and <strong>remaining honey</strong> in a small bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
