    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> cornflour</strong> and <strong>smoked paprika</strong> in a large bowl with the <strong>ground coriander</strong>, <strong>cracked black pepper</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped fable mushrooms </strong>and mix until fully combined</p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and stir it all together – these are your <strong>coated mushrooms</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
